title: All Too Well (10 Minute Version) (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
The time has come.. We get to break down Taylor's masterpiece, ATWTMVTVFTV! AHHHHHH!! There's so much to discuss, to fangirl over, and there are several things that we add to our list of questions to ask Taylor! Plus, a special giveaway!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us?
